---
import Layout from "../../components/Layout.astro";
import Mark from "../../components/Mark.astro";
import TextGenerating from "../../components/react/TextGenerating";
import LatestProjects from "../../components/LatestProjects.astro";
---

<Layout>
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4">
        <main class="lg:relative">
          <div
            class="mx-auto max-w-7xl w-fulltext-center lg:text-left"
          >
            <div class="pt-16 px-4 lg:w-1/2 sm:px-8 xl:pr-16">
              <h1
                class="text-4xl tracking-tight font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-6xl"
              >
                <span class="block gradient-text xl:inline">Legacy Software!</span>
                <TextGenerating client:load className="block xl:inline" words="Start building again — without limitations" />
              </h1>
              <p
                class="mt-3 max-w-md mx-auto text-lg text-gray-500 sm:text-xl md:mt-5 md:max-w-3xl"
              >
                Has your original developer vanished into thin air? Then it's time to let Vectos support, improve, or rebuild your legacy application—so you can move forward with confidence.
              </p>
              
            </div>
          </div>
          <div
            class="hidden md:block relative w-full h-64 sm:h-72 md:h-96 lg:absolute lg:inset-y-0 lg:right-0 lg:w-1/2 lg:h-full"
          >
            <img
              src="/img/services/legacy/hero.png"
              alt=""
            />
          </div>
        </main>

        <!-- The Real Cost of Legacy Software Section -->
        <div class="mt-6 py-6">
          <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
                The Real Cost of Legacy Software
              </h2>
              <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
                Don't underestimate the hidden costs of outdated systems
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-4 p-6 bg-red-50 border-l-4 border-red-400 rounded-lg shadow-sm mb-8">
              <p class="text-lg font-bold text-red-700 mb-4">These aren't just minor annoyances. They're roadblocks that can stall your growth:</p>
              <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-base text-red-900 space-y-2 font-semibold">
                  <li>No in-house expertise — problems linger and escalate</li>
                  <li>Security vulnerabilities put your data and business at risk</li>
                  <li>Inefficient workflows drain productivity and frustrate your team</li>
                  <li>No cloud or mobile access — remote work becomes impossible</li>   
                  <li>Integrations with modern tools are broken or impossible</li>
                </ul>
                <ul class="list-disc list-inside text-base text-red-900 space-y-2 font-semibold">
                  <li>Compliance becomes a ticking time bomb</li>
                  <li>Hard to attract developers — nobody wants outdated code</li>
                  <li>Scaling is painful or impossible</li>
                  <li>Maintenance costs keep rising</li>
                  <li>Customer experience suffers from slow, clunky service</li>
                </ul>
              </div>
              <p class="mt-4 text-base text-red-800 font-medium">The longer you wait, the bigger the impact on your growth, costs, and reputation.</p>
            </div>
            
            <p class="text-center text-lg font-semibold text-indigo-700">Let's change that. Together. With Vectos.</p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- What We Deliver Section -->
        <div class="mt-6 py-6">
          <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center mb-12">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
                What Modernizing Your Legacy Software Delivers
              </h2>
              <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
                Moving to the cloud is just the beginning. Here's what you really gain:
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-12 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3">
              <!-- Efficiency Card -->
              <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-blue-500 to-indigo-600 h-2"></div>
                <div class="p-8">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-blue-100 rounded-lg mb-6">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-blue-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Efficiency That Saves Time</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Legacy systems often underperform—slow, clunky, and frustrating. We optimize your app for the cloud, unlocking serious performance gains and saving your team valuable time every day.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- User Experience Card -->
              <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-green-500 to-emerald-600 h-2"></div>
                <div class="p-8">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-green-100 rounded-lg mb-6">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-green-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197m13.5-9a2.5 2.5 0 11-5 0 2.5 2.5 0 015 0z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Happier Users, Stronger Teams</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Old software slows people down—and that frustration adds up. A modern, intuitive interface improves productivity, boosts morale, and helps retain talent.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Integration Card -->
              <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-purple-500 to-pink-600 h-2"></div>
                <div class="p-8">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg mb-6">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-purple-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8.25 3v1.5M4.5 8.25H3m18 0h-1.5M4.5 12H3m18 0h-1.5m-15 3.75H3m18 0h-1.5M8.25 19.5V21M12 3v1.5m0 15V21m3.75-18v1.5m0 15V21m-9-1.5h10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25-2.25V6.75a2.25 2.25 0 0 0-2.25-2.25H6.75A2.25 2.25 0 0 0 4.5 6.75v10.5a2.25 2.25 0 0 0 2.25 2.25Zm.75-12h9v9h-9v-9Z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Seamless Integration</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Modernizing your app opens the door to powerful integrations. Once it's cloud-ready, it's easier to connect with other tools and expand functionality faster.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Security Card -->
              <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-red-500 to-orange-600 h-2"></div>
                <div class="p-8">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-red-100 rounded-lg mb-6">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-red-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 15v2m-6 4h12a2 2 0 002-2v-6a2 2 0 00-2-2H6a2 2 0 00-2 2v6a2 2 0 002 2zm10-10V7a4 4 0 00-8 0v4h8z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Enhanced Security</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Security updates and patches are handled automatically—keeping your application secure, stable, and compliant with modern standards.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Cost Predictability Card -->
              <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-teal-500 to-cyan-600 h-2"></div>
                <div class="p-8">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-teal-100 rounded-lg mb-6">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-teal-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 8c-1.657 0-3 .895-3 2s1.343 2 3 2 3 .895 3 2-1.343 2-3 2m0-8c1.11 0 2.08.402 2.599 1M12 8V7m0 1v8m0 0v1m0-1c-1.11 0-2.08-.402-2.599-1"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Predictable Costs</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Say goodbye to surprise expenses. Cloud hosting and support come with transparent, predictable monthly costs that scale with your business.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Scalability Card -->
              <div class="bg-white rounded-xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-300">
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-yellow-500 to-orange-600 h-2"></div>
                <div class="p-8">
                  <div class="flex items-center justify-center w-16 h-16 bg-yellow-100 rounded-lg mb-6">
                    <svg class="w-8 h-8 text-yellow-600" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                      <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M7 12l3-3 3 3 4-4M8 21l4-4 4 4M3 4h18M4 4h16v12a1 1 0 01-1 1H5a1 1 0 01-1-1V4z"></path>
                    </svg>
                  </div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-4">Future-Proof Scalability</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Modern architecture that grows with your business. No more technical limitations holding back your expansion plans.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <LatestProjects />

        <!-- Process Section -->
        <div class="mt-8 py-8 bg-gray-50">
          <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">
                Our Legacy Modernization Process
              </h2>
              <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-600">
                A clear phase model — you decide how far you want to go
              </p>
            </div>
            
            <div class="mt-16 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4">
              <!-- Phase 1 -->
              <div class="relative bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border-t-4 border-indigo-500">
                <div class="absolute -top-4 left-6 bg-indigo-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">
                  1
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Assessment & Discovery</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Map out your current systems, pain points, and opportunities for improvement. Understand your starting point.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Phase 2 -->
              <div class="relative bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border-t-4 border-blue-500">
                <div class="absolute -top-4 left-6 bg-blue-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">
                  2
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Vision & Strategy</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Set a clear future state and create a practical roadmap to get there. Define where you're going.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Phase 3 -->
              <div class="relative bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border-t-4 border-green-500">
                <div class="absolute -top-4 left-6 bg-green-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">
                  3
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Stabilization</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Fix critical issues and improve stability to create a safe launchpad for transformation.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Phase 4 -->
              <div class="relative bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border-t-4 border-purple-500">
                <div class="absolute -top-4 left-6 bg-purple-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">
                  4
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Modularization</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Decouple the monolith and isolate parts that can be modernized step by step.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Phase 5 -->
              <div class="relative bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border-t-4 border-red-500">
                <div class="absolute -top-4 left-6 bg-red-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">
                  5
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Rebuild or Replace</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Refactor, rewrite, or replace components with scalable, maintainable solutions.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Phase 6 -->
              <div class="relative bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border-t-4 border-yellow-500">
                <div class="absolute -top-4 left-6 bg-yellow-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">
                  6
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Testing & Validation</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Test extensively and get user feedback to ensure quality and reliability.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Phase 7 -->
              <div class="relative bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border-t-4 border-teal-500">
                <div class="absolute -top-4 left-6 bg-teal-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">
                  7
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Deployment</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Roll out the new system to the cloud to cut costs and improve performance.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>

              <!-- Phase 8 -->
              <div class="relative bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg p-6 border-t-4 border-pink-500">
                <div class="absolute -top-4 left-6 bg-pink-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold text-lg">
                  8
                </div>
                <div class="mt-4">
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Monitoring & Optimization</h3>
                  <p class="text-gray-600">
                    Track performance, fix issues fast, and evolve your platform over time.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="text-center mt-12">
              <p class="text-lg text-indigo-700 font-semibold">Each phase builds on the last—step by step, toward a future-proof platform.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <Mark />
    </div>
</Layout>